# ============================================================================
# SECURITY BEST PRACTICES
# ============================================================================
#
# ✅ DO:
#   - Use strong, unique JWT_SECRET_KEY (32+ characters)
#   - Set DEBUG=false in production
#   - Restrict CORS_ORIGINS to your actual domains
#   - Enable SSL for database connections (?sslmode=require)
#   - Rotate JWT_SECRET_KEY periodically
#   - Use environment-specific databases (dev/staging/prod)
#
# ❌ DON'T:
#   - Commit .env files with real credentials to Git
#   - Use default/example JWT secrets in production
#   - Set CORS_ORIGINS=* in production (security risk)
#   - Share your DATABASE_URL publicly
#   - Use the same JWT_SECRET_KEY across environments
#
# ============================================================================
